    "text": [
        "Advanced technology has significantly changed the way people interact with each other these days. This essay will explain how advancements in technology has affected our daily life and discuss if these changes make a positive impact on us.",
        "Many aspects in our life have been changed because of technology. In the past, people only have limited ways like writing letters to communicate as there are various difficulties such as long distance or language barriers. However, advanced technology enables us to communicate more efficiently and effectively because it provides us more options to interact including email, phone call and video chat. To illustrate, when I was traveling in Thailand 10 years ago, I had to go to a payphone if I want to make a phone call to my parents but now, I can just video chat with them on my smartphone. As can be seen, the way of interaction has been deeply changed with the development of technology.",
        "Interaction plays a crucial role in our society and we are able to communicate more easily and effortlessly compared to the past due to advancements in technology. However, it\u2019s been criticized that people tend to be unsociable because of social media like Facebook and Wechat are being widely used so people don\u2019t have many opportunity or motivation to go out and socialize with their friends and family. For this reason, some people perceive advancements in technology can be detrimental to shape people\u2019s personality.",
        "To sum up, many aspects of our life especially ways of communication have been changed nowadays. I am inclined to say that the overall benefits of these changes are superior."
